  "body": "We can't break admin_nodeInfo (for compatibility reasons) - there are specs exist, etc... \r\nBut admin_nodeInfo is not enough flexible for Erigon. Difference is:\r\n- erigon can have multiple sentries\r\n- each sentry can serve 1 P2P protocol\r\n- can run many sentries which serve same P2P protocol \r\n\r\nCreate erigon_nodeInfo method which will return list of objects (returned by admin_nodeInfo). \r\nDefault sort by: (name, enode)\r\nAdd also method admin_nodeInfo - it will just return first object from list above. \r\n \r\n",
